da9cf021-0066-4435-82e5-b941f9e4945c.1270d5e9-9479-4d94-bd79-b5e9b3c39412.description=
This operation updates MSS DRDB screen

Inputs\:
   queryInput - result of query automation Database(1 row) 

Results\:
   errorMessages - MSS screen update result
  draftBsbFlag - flag value is set to True if thereis  error
   draftAccountFlag - flag value is set to true


Responses\:
    Success – Proceed to Update ACHC in MSS
Failure – Proceed to Check For MSS Loading Errors
Rework - goto Check for rework flags
